{"tid":389033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰漢慘遭蟹鉗男人最痛　瘋狂尖叫痛不欲生","createTime":"2017-09-06T01:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T01:47:22.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e0d2193b19f4b251889cf1853a214778174f69","tid":389033,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:38:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>泰漢慘遭蟹鉗男人最痛　瘋狂尖叫痛不欲生</strong><br />\n<br />\n一段相信於泰國拍得的影片顯示，一名男子早前於一個戶外水池中被蟹襲擊，下體被鉗着緊緊不放，隨即不斷尖叫，痛不欲生；身旁友人則一直嘗試將蟹拉走。<br />\n<br />\n男子被拉出水面時，清晰可見他的下體被蟹鉗着。最後眾人雖然成功把牠拉走，但鉗子仍舊緊鉗男子的下體，與蟹的軀體分離。據悉，男子當時下水數秒後，已經遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170905%2Fbknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html&d=6hPYI1bzOCvKS%2BKbsFK6bQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ab6967d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985de560ddcf58886f4f2027c9df6b957f3bf8bf","tid":389033,"uid":37522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>泰漢慘遭蟹鉗男人最痛　瘋狂尖叫痛不欲生</strong><br />\n<br />\n一段相信於泰國拍得的影片顯示，一名男子早前於一個戶外水池中被蟹襲擊，下體被鉗着緊緊不放，隨即不斷尖叫，痛不欲生；身旁友人則一直嘗試將蟹拉走。<br />\n<br />\n男子被拉出水面時，清晰可見他的下體被蟹鉗着。最後眾人雖然成功把牠拉走，但鉗子仍舊緊鉗男子的下體，與蟹的軀體分離。據悉，男子當時下水數秒後，已經遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170905%2Fbknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html&d=6hPYI1bzOCvKS%2BKbsFK6bQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ab6967d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170905/bknint-20170905163644184-0905_17011_001.html</a><br 